331
00:13:37,570 --> 00:13:37,775
 

332
00:13:37,775 --> 00:13:39,254
qu'il le veuille ou non.

333
00:13:39,254 --> 00:13:45,855
 

334
00:13:45,855 --> 00:13:48,608
- Bonjour.
- Bonjour. Tu veux un bon café.

335
00:13:48,608 --> 00:13:48,855
 

336
00:13:48,855 --> 00:13:50,368
Non merci.

337
00:13:50,368 --> 00:13:50,655
 

338
00:13:50,655 --> 00:13:53,374
