349
00:14:14,892 --> 00:14:15,135
 

350
00:14:15,135 --> 00:14:18,047
- C'est gentil.
- On va commencer petit et simple.

351
00:14:18,047 --> 00:14:18,855
 

352
00:14:18,855 --> 00:14:20,971
Tu voudrais un chat ? Un bébé ?

353
00:14:20,971 --> 00:14:22,255
 

354
