365
00:14:40,923 --> 00:14:41,135
 

366
00:14:41,135 --> 00:14:44,491
Angel, j'espère me tromper là-dessus,
mais à mon avis. . .

367
00:14:44,491 --> 00:14:44,695
 

368
00:14:44,695 --> 00:14:46,686
il est temps de consulter les Oracles.

369
00:14:46,686 --> 00:14:46,935
 

370
00:14:46,935 --> 00:14:48,448
C'est inutile.

371
00:14:48,448 --> 00:14:49,455
 

372
00:14:49,455 --> 00:14:51,173
Tu dois y réfléchir.

373
00:14:51,173 --> 00:14:58,535
 

374
00:14:58,535 --> 00:14:59,934
Les Oracles.

375
00:14:59,934 --> 00:15:00,855
 

376
00:15:00,855 --> 00:15:01,970
Sortir en douce.

377
00:15:01,970 --> 00:15:03,335
 

378
