517
00:26:46,372 --> 00:26:46,895
 

518
00:26:46,895 --> 00:26:48,965
- Non ! Revenez !
- Trouve le rouleau !

519
00:26:48,965 --> 00:26:49,655
 

520
00:26:49,655 --> 00:26:52,852
