pouvoir d'ôter la marque et la sauver.

521
00:26:52,852 --> 00:26:53,415
 

522
00:26:53,415 --> 00:26:56,327
- Où est-il, il doit payer.
- ll est ici pour la renaissance.

523
00:26:56,327 --> 00:26:56,535
 

524
00:26:56,535 --> 00:26:57,411
La renaissance ?

525
00:26:57,411 --> 00:26:57,615
 

526
00:26:57,615 --> 00:27:01,130
Comme ses semblables,
il se cache derrière la loi.

527
00:27:01,130 --> 00:27:01,455
 

528
00:27:01,455 --> 00:27:03,047
Combats-le !

529
00:27:03,047 --> 00:27:05,815
 

530
